{"tid":668964,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"睇 書 學攝影","createTime":"2018-05-18T05:25:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-18T10:00:38.000Z","uid":185452,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a6abb71adb7aaa8e71637329b996d6bb140952b1","tid":668964,"uid":185452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T05:25:39.000Z","msg":"上次開 post，多謝大家嘅支持！<br />\n<br />\n睇 youtube 學攝影<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/655488/page/2\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/655488/page/2</a><br />\n<br />\n今次拋磚引玉，分享下睇過嘅書。 <br />\n<br />\nMichael Freeman 出過好多書，在 政府圖書館都有得借。有啲有中文版。<br />\n<br />\n其中一本叫 &ldquo;The photographers mind. Creative thinking for better digital photos&rdquo;，特別好睇！<br />\n<br />\n當中有一章，詳細講述佢構圖嘅過程，如何反復構思，去突出當刻 最有趣嘅點。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/NZeBktq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FNZeBktq.jpg&h=f9975bc8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n現場環境<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/0BIqsuw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F0BIqsuw.jpg&h=7fb9af06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上方照片是 最終嘅選圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/hLsofsb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FhLsofsb.jpg&h=15554bdc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最下方是 最終選圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/WeXmnac.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FWeXmnac.jpg&h=b0781629&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n講述構圖嘅平衡元素<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/uSqgU8x.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FuSqgU8x.jpg&h=33ea82dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n網上有 ebook，有興趣，可自行搜查 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bd16bb23b3be607e8aded7097604a3615678cf5","tid":668964,"uid":72240,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T06:17:28.000Z","msg":"有無中文<img src=\"